      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-broadens-roles-sales-executives-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社周二看到的一份内部备忘录中称，摩根大通已扩大其销售部门部分高管的职责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-broadens-roles-sales-executives-2024-04-30/</guid>
